---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import profileImg from '../images/profile.jpeg';
import premiaImg1 from '../images/premia-1.jpeg';
import premiaImg2 from '../images/premia-2.jpeg';
import premiaImg3 from '../images/premia-3.jpeg';
import premiaImg4 from '../images/premia-4.jpeg';
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-primary-500 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Who I am</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-2">About Me</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 mx-auto w-16 h-1 bg-accent-400 rounded-full"></div>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg text-center leading-relaxed max-w-[720px] mt-4 mx-auto">
        I’m a Computer Engineer graduated from the Universidad Nacional de Tucumán, Argentina, 
        currently living in Premià de Mar, Barcelona.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

      <!-- Left: photo mosaic collage -->
      <div class="relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative w-[300px] h-[360px] sm:w-[380px] sm:h-[440px]">

          <!-- 4 background mosaic tiles -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[130px] h-[158px] sm:w-[168px] sm:h-[204px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg -rotate-3 border-2 border-white">
            <Image src={premiaImg1} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[130px] h-[158px] sm:w-[168px] sm:h-[204px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg rotate-2 border-2 border-white">
            <Image src={premiaImg3} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-left-top" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[130px] h-[158px] sm:w-[168px] sm:h-[204px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg rotate-1 border-2 border-white">
            <Image src={premiaImg2} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[130px] h-[158px] sm:w-[168px] sm:h-[204px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg -rotate-2 border-2 border-white">
            <Image src={premiaImg4} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-right-top" />
          </div>

          <!-- Main profile card — centered, layered on top -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="w-[148px] h-[188px] sm:w-52 sm:h-64 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white">
                <Image src={profileImg} alt="Bruno Cesano" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
              </div>
              <!-- Badges -->
              <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-8 bg-accent-400 text-slate-900 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-md rotate-3 whitespace-nowrap">
                Open to work
              </div>
              <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-8 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-md -rotate-2 whitespace-nowrap">
                3+ years exp.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: text content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Over the last 3 years, I’ve been working as a Full Stack Developer, 
          focusing on building web applications and enjoying every stage of the software 
          development process. Although I work across the stack, I naturally feel more 
          connected to software development and backend-oriented problem solving.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Throughout my experience, I’ve worked on both short and long-term projects 
          involving large volumes of data, real-time maintenance, and end-to-end feature
          development. These experiences helped me develop not only technical skills, but 
          also adaptability and a product-oriented mindset.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          I enjoy learning, improving continuously, and building solutions that create real value. 
          Currently, I’m open to new opportunities where I can keep growing and contribute as part 
          of a great team.
        </p>

        <!-- Highlight cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2">
          <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-2xl p-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-primary-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-sm">Clean Code</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Readable, maintainable, tested</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-accent-300/20 border border-accent-300/40 rounded-2xl p-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-800" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-sm">Problem Solver</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Analytical &amp; creative thinking</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-2xl p-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-sm">Performance</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Fast, optimized experiences</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-accent-300/20 border border-accent-300/40 rounded-2xl p-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-sm">Collaboration</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Team-oriented mindset</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors"
        >
          Let's work together
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
